short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Turning YApi docs into Admate codes

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: YApi2Code is a code generator aiming at turning YApi ( https://github.com/ymfe/yapi ) docs into codes which applies to Admate ( a front-end framework for admin interfaces ).
